RbtwsLicenseFeature.name: RbtwsLicenseFeature
RbtwsLicenseFeature.description: Enumeration of the licensable features. Currently only 1 feature is licensed, the number AP/DAPs concurrently supported. This feature has 'three' levels: none, 1, and 2. Level 1 implies support for 80 concurrent AP/DAPs, level 2 implies support for 120 concurrent AP/DAPs. The value in object rbtwsLicenseInfoEntryValue should therefore reflect the number of AP/DAPs supported.

rbtwsSerialNumber.name: rbtwsSerialNumber
rbtwsSerialNumber.description: The serial number of the switch.

rbtwsSwMajorVersionNumber.name: rbtwsSwMajorVersionNumber
rbtwsSwMajorVersionNumber.description: The major release version of the running software.

rbtwsSwMinorVersionNumber.name: rbtwsSwMinorVersionNumber
rbtwsSwMinorVersionNumber.description: The minor release version of the running software.

rbtwsVersionString.name: rbtwsVersionString
rbtwsVersionString.description: The version string of the running software, including the major, minor, patch and build numbers, such as 3.0.0.185

rbtwsMobilityDomainName.name: rbtwsMobilityDomainName
rbtwsMobilityDomainName.description: The mobility domain containing the switch, or a zero-length string when the mobility domain is unknown.

rbtwsMobilitySeedIp.name: rbtwsMobilitySeedIp
rbtwsMobilitySeedIp.description: The IPv4 address of the seed switch for this switch's mobility domain, or the IPv4 address 0.0.0.0 if unknown.

rbtwsMobilityMemberTableSize.name: rbtwsMobilityMemberTableSize
rbtwsMobilityMemberTableSize.description: The number of entries in the mobility member table, rbtwsMobilityMemberTable.

rbtwsMobilityMemberTable.name: rbtwsMobilityMemberTable
rbtwsMobilityMemberTable.description: Table of members of the mobility domain, indexed by the member IPv4 address.

rbtwsMobilityMemberEntry.name: rbtwsMobilityMemberEntry
rbtwsMobilityMemberEntry.description: An entry in the rbtwsMobilityMemberTable table.

rbtwsMobilityMemberEntryAddr.name: rbtwsMobilityMemberEntryAddr
rbtwsMobilityMemberEntryAddr.description: IPv4 address of a member of the mobility domain.

rbtwsLicenseInfoTableSize.name: rbtwsLicenseInfoTableSize
rbtwsLicenseInfoTableSize.description: The number of entries in the license table, rbtwsLicenseInfoTable.

rbtwsLicenseInfoTable.name: rbtwsLicenseInfoTable
rbtwsLicenseInfoTable.description: Table of installed licenses on the switch. The licences provide additional capabilities over the default capabilities of the switch.

rbtwsLicenseInfoEntryValue.name: rbtwsLicenseInfoEntryValue
rbtwsLicenseInfoEntryValue.description: The value of the feature enabled, for example a feature may have multiple levels of licensing, so the value will very with the license level.

rbtwsLicenseInfoEntryDescr.name: rbtwsLicenseInfoEntryDescr
rbtwsLicenseInfoEntryDescr.description: A human interpretable description of this license, for example, '120 APs or DAPs.'
